<Glow Size="200" Top="-200px" Blur="100" Left="calc(50% - 100px)" ShadowColor="var(--primary)" />
<Glow Size="80" Top="800px" Blur="100" Left="0" ShadowColor="var(--primary)" />

<div class="position-relative d-flex flex-column" style="z-index: 30">
	<a href="@WebRoutes.Info.HelpCenter" class="font-white"><i class="bi bi-chevron-left"></i> Back to Help Center</a>

	<h2 class="mt-5 mb-5">A great workplace combines exceptional colleagues and challenging challenges.</h2>

	<div class="mt-3 mb-3"></div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<h3>Freedom and responsibility</h3>
			<p class="mt-2 font-sm">
				Our main philosophy is people over process. Our culture has been instrumental in our success and has helped us attract and retain great colleagues, making working here even more enjoyable.
			</p>
			<a href="/" class="button button-fit py-2 px-4 font-white">Read about our culture</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row mt-5 justify-content-end">
		<div class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column align-items-start align-items-md-end">
			<h3 class="text-start text-md-end">Streaming entertainment. Global original content. Personalization of products.</h3>
			<p class="mt-2 font-sm text-start text-md-end">
				Our first original series debuted in 2024. Over the coming decades, streaming TV will replace linear TV, and we hope to maintain our leadership by offering an amazing entertainment experience.
			</p>
			<a href="/" class="button button-fit py-2 px-4 font-white">Let's see what happens next</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="mt-5 mb-5"></div>

</div>

